The paper proposes a K-best model enumeration algorithm for Support Vector Machines (SVM) that is useful in supporting users' interactive examination of their requirements on enumerated models. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE).
